WEBVTT

01:36.979 --> 01:40.840
[The Best Thing]

01:41.479 --> 01:48.850
[Episode 2: Apple—Sweet in taste, sour, and cool in nature.
It benefits the stomach, generates body fluids, relieves irritation, and helps with sobering up]

01:49.479 --> 01:52.890
I quite like this girl.

01:53.630 --> 01:55.070
She's quite good-looking.

01:55.759 --> 01:57.759
She has a nice temperament, elegant and refined,

01:57.990 --> 01:59.400
matching my taste.

02:00.440 --> 02:01.570
She's four years younger than you.

02:01.570 --> 02:03.240
Age-wise, it's also a good match.

02:05.720 --> 02:07.210
Are you listening?

02:09.240 --> 02:10.610
I'm listening.

02:11.050 --> 02:13.170
But you don't have to push me like that.

02:14.550 --> 02:16.840
I'm just asking you to get her phone number.

02:16.870 --> 02:18.460
You know, you could greet her daily,

02:18.520 --> 02:20.360
check in, and show care.

02:20.610 --> 02:23.010
Otherwise, you will only be able to see her

02:23.010 --> 02:24.490
once a week during the follow-up visit.

02:24.490 --> 02:26.730
How would she ever notice you?

02:28.520 --> 02:29.360
I mean, come on.

02:30.770 --> 02:31.680
You're not even worried about it.

02:32.610 --> 02:34.079
You're already 31

02:34.560 --> 02:36.290
and still don't have a girlfriend.

02:36.730 --> 02:37.120
You...

02:37.680 --> 02:39.329
It's precisely because I'm 31

02:40.079 --> 02:41.680
that I'm being stricter with myself

02:41.680 --> 02:42.960
and more cautious.

02:43.770 --> 02:44.640
This is being responsible

02:44.640 --> 02:46.290
to both myself and others.

02:47.450 --> 02:48.940
I can't be like my dad,

02:49.010 --> 02:50.960
marrying someone and then neglecting her, can I?

03:00.490 --> 03:01.450
Your mother...

03:01.450 --> 03:03.360
Indeed, we were too hasty back then.

03:05.010 --> 03:06.840
But you're being too cautious, aren't you?

03:10.930 --> 03:14.170
If you want to be a lifelong bachelor, then go ahead.

03:15.560 --> 03:17.210
I won't say more. Do as you please.

03:23.290 --> 03:24.360
Don't worry.

03:24.770 --> 03:25.930
I'll handle

03:26.170 --> 03:27.400
this matter myself.

03:30.210 --> 03:31.520
What do you mean by "handle it"?

03:33.420 --> 03:34.540
This girl...

03:34.930 --> 03:36.210
I think she's quite pretty too.

03:36.730 --> 03:38.610
And she's also my type.

03:40.290 --> 03:41.170
Shallow.

03:42.730 --> 03:43.240
Fine.

03:43.770 --> 03:44.680
I'm shallow.

03:44.890 --> 03:45.800
You're not shallow.

03:46.079 --> 03:47.240
You're a gentleman.

03:49.210 --> 03:50.240
I'm shallow, I'm shallow.

04:17.370 --> 04:19.110
[Li Jie]

04:19.529 --> 04:20.850
You brat.

04:20.850 --> 04:22.530
You made me miss my rounds yesterday.

04:47.440 --> 04:48.490
I slept well.

04:58.130 --> 04:58.890
Thank you, Auntie.

04:58.909 --> 04:59.510
You're welcome.

05:10.920 --> 05:12.130
This patient has laryngeal cancer,

05:12.160 --> 05:14.680
experiencing difficulty swallowing after radiotherapy.

05:14.850 --> 05:16.240
From the X-ray,

05:16.240 --> 05:17.410
there's local stenosis.

05:18.090 --> 05:19.290
I think putting in a stent would fix it.

05:19.530 --> 05:20.440
No.

05:20.760 --> 05:22.320
The upper part of the esophagus is narrowed.

05:22.320 --> 05:23.170
If we insert a stent,

05:23.170 --> 05:24.240
the patient will feel a foreign body sensation.

05:25.000 --> 05:25.970
It'd be very uncomfortable.

05:25.970 --> 05:27.760
Also, considering the patient's advanced age,

05:28.170 --> 05:30.410
we need to first determine if it's tumor recurrence

05:30.410 --> 05:32.650
or post-radiation local scarring and contraction

05:32.650 --> 05:33.730
before deciding on treatment.

05:34.170 --> 05:35.760
If the patient's physical condition allows,

05:36.000 --> 05:37.409
we can first use phlegm-dissolving medication,

05:37.680 --> 05:39.880
then combine it with cupping and bloodletting on back pressure points.

05:40.290 --> 05:43.200
You want to use acupuncture to alleviate the patient's symptoms?

05:43.360 --> 05:43.970
More or less.

05:49.090 --> 05:49.560
That could work.

05:49.930 --> 05:50.880
I think it could work.

05:50.880 --> 05:51.800
It's feasible.

05:52.560 --> 05:53.120
Hello.

05:53.650 --> 05:54.760
This is okay.

05:54.970 --> 05:56.000
Give me the medical record first.

06:00.140 --> 06:01.470
Kexin!

06:01.800 --> 06:02.680
Give me the medical record.

06:02.680 --> 06:03.240
I'll take it over first.

06:03.240 --> 06:04.680
I've finished it here.

06:04.680 --> 06:05.240
You can take it over first.

06:05.240 --> 06:05.760
Oh, okay.

06:05.760 --> 06:06.850
Line up properly.

06:06.850 --> 06:08.170
No rush.

06:20.560 --> 06:21.440
Are there many patients today?

06:22.000 --> 06:22.410
Yes.

06:33.409 --> 06:34.250
[Front Office]

06:37.280 --> 06:38.110
[Front Office; Shen Xifan]

06:45.170 --> 06:47.630
[Staff Canteen]

06:59.850 --> 07:00.680
Suye,

07:01.120 --> 07:02.320
have a chicken leg.

07:09.090 --> 07:10.200
You're being suspiciously nice.

07:11.000 --> 07:12.090
Just say what you want.

07:14.650 --> 07:15.090
Suye.

07:16.200 --> 07:17.880
In the comments you gave on my thesis,

07:18.410 --> 07:20.200
why did you put a cross

07:20.200 --> 07:21.360
above my name?

07:23.200 --> 07:24.850
Do you have some opinions

07:24.850 --> 07:26.490
or suggestions about me as a person?

07:28.760 --> 07:29.650
Shouldn't you already know

07:29.650 --> 07:30.850
what I think about you?

07:37.000 --> 07:39.409
Have this shrimp and go think about it.

07:40.820 --> 07:41.770
Shrimp.

07:49.680 --> 07:51.440
You didn't answer the phone when I tried to reach you.

08:11.200 --> 08:11.930
Hello, Manager Shen.

08:11.930 --> 08:12.320
Hello.

08:13.650 --> 08:14.530
Hello, Manager Shen.

08:14.530 --> 08:14.850
I'm off work.

08:14.850 --> 08:15.320
Manager Shen, hello.

08:15.320 --> 08:16.000
Manager Shen, you're off work?

08:16.200 --> 08:16.930
Bye-bye.

08:18.290 --> 08:18.680
Look,

08:18.880 --> 08:20.360
that guy outside is her boyfriend, right?

08:25.120 --> 08:26.120
I'm leaving now.

08:26.480 --> 08:27.210
Bye-bye.

08:30.530 --> 08:31.610
Why didn't you answer the phone?

08:31.960 --> 08:33.240
I was busy with work.

08:33.500 --> 08:35.030
Why did you come to pick me up today?

08:35.960 --> 08:36.679
You didn't answer your phone,

08:36.679 --> 08:37.600
so how would I know if you had forgotten

08:37.600 --> 08:38.600
that we were supposed to have dinner together today?

08:39.360 --> 08:41.049
I wrote it in my memo.

08:50.170 --> 08:51.250
Manager Shen's boyfriend?

08:58.200 --> 08:59.800
Where did she find her boyfriend?

09:00.410 --> 09:00.960
Back in university.

09:18.690 --> 09:26.130
♫Love love love love, is right in front of me♫

09:26.810 --> 09:34.500
♫Ooh love, ooh love, I've seen your face♫

09:35.060 --> 09:42.320
♫Love love love love, is talking right at me♫

09:42.620 --> 09:49.570
♫Loving you, loving you, is the best thing I'll ever do♫

09:54.080 --> 09:55.600
Can you not use your phone while eating?

10:00.130 --> 10:01.440
When I was abroad,

10:01.890 --> 10:03.280
we called each other hundreds of times every day.

10:04.130 --> 10:05.480
Now I'm sitting right in front of you,

10:05.930 --> 10:07.010
yet you still have to use your phone?

10:08.010 --> 10:10.480
Xiangya has been working on improving the hotel's Western cuisine recently.

10:11.100 --> 10:12.490
I want to take a photo

10:12.560 --> 10:13.800
for her to reference.

10:14.130 --> 10:15.480
Why is she working so hard?

10:15.840 --> 10:16.840
While she's young,

10:17.250 --> 10:18.600
she should just hurry up and marry a trust fund boy.

10:21.650 --> 10:23.130
Xiangya is indeed beautiful.

10:23.770 --> 10:25.130
She has many suitors.

10:25.650 --> 10:26.410
But...

10:26.800 --> 10:28.560
she's also working hard.

10:29.370 --> 10:30.010
Is that so?

10:33.250 --> 10:34.930
You two are really good friends.

10:36.650 --> 10:37.720
One is working hard in her career,

10:38.600 --> 10:39.480
while the other is striving to study abroad.

10:44.770 --> 10:46.550
I just have this plan.

10:47.170 --> 10:48.880
I haven't even applied to schools yet.

10:51.680 --> 10:52.480
Yan Heng,

10:52.890 --> 10:54.290
you've finally come back to the country.

10:54.890 --> 10:57.300
Let's not argue about this, okay?

10:57.370 --> 10:59.530
Do I have to wait until you're already abroad

10:59.530 --> 11:00.650
before I start getting angry?

11:07.560 --> 11:08.080
Xifan,

11:09.130 --> 11:10.080
after we get married,

11:10.960 --> 11:12.410
do you still want to continue in this industry?

11:14.440 --> 11:16.410
It's ultimately just a service industry.

11:17.840 --> 11:18.930
When my future business partners

11:18.930 --> 11:20.130
stay at your hotel,

11:20.330 --> 11:22.400
you'll have to cater to them like a servant, right?

11:28.890 --> 11:29.560
Let's do this.

11:30.660 --> 11:31.930
Quit your job tomorrow.

11:33.530 --> 11:34.440
And forget about studying abroad.

11:34.730 --> 11:36.760
After all, you're putting in all this effort to study abroad

11:36.790 --> 11:38.710
just to learn about hotel services, right?

11:45.490 --> 11:46.400
I...

11:46.860 --> 11:49.060
have always had this plan to study abroad.

11:50.050 --> 11:51.770
It's just that when we graduated from college,

11:52.480 --> 11:54.320
you said Switzerland was too far away

11:54.560 --> 11:55.960
and inconvenient for you to visit me.

11:56.410 --> 11:57.050
So...

11:57.770 --> 11:58.800
If you put it that way,

11:59.460 --> 12:00.340
dating me

12:00.360 --> 12:02.120
is hindering you from becoming a hotel tycoon, huh?

12:03.290 --> 12:04.770
That's not what I meant.

12:05.130 --> 12:06.320
You've misunderstood.

12:08.770 --> 12:10.010
I just love you too much.

12:10.500 --> 12:12.740
That's why I didn't realize you've always been so selfish.

12:18.480 --> 12:19.200
Look,

12:19.530 --> 12:20.770
you've been so busy lately.

12:21.050 --> 12:22.720
Tonight, you finally have some time.

12:23.370 --> 12:24.800
Let me show you my course schedule.

12:24.800 --> 12:25.440
Stop it.

12:28.840 --> 12:29.560
Yes, it's me.

12:31.410 --> 12:32.860
Let me go to a quieter place to talk with you.

12:51.390 --> 12:52.360
The barbecue is here.

12:53.920 --> 12:54.970
Quick, eat it while it's hot.

12:56.120 --> 12:58.510
Besides barbecue, I want to eat something else.

12:59.030 --> 13:00.430
All this barbecue isn't enough for you?

13:01.370 --> 13:03.050
I want to have Cantonese cuisine.

13:03.050 --> 13:03.800
I want shrimp dumplings.

13:04.010 --> 13:04.650
Rock, paper, scissors.

13:04.650 --> 13:05.410
If you win, I'll buy it for you.

13:06.560 --> 13:07.600
Impressive.

13:07.800 --> 13:08.480
One more time.

13:09.410 --> 13:10.010
Rock, paper, scissors.

13:10.010 --> 13:10.560
Two baskets.

13:11.440 --> 13:14.170
Rock, paper, scissors!

13:15.170 --> 13:16.130
Ms. Shen?

13:17.410 --> 13:19.530
Didn't you go out on a date with Yan?

13:19.530 --> 13:20.800
Why are you back so early?

13:25.250 --> 13:27.960
We just had a simple meal.

13:28.200 --> 13:30.290
He had something to do, so he left to take care of it first.

13:30.290 --> 13:31.130
He finally came back for once

13:31.130 --> 13:31.960
and still has things to do?

13:31.960 --> 13:32.640
Yeah.

13:32.800 --> 13:33.890
You must not have eaten enough then.

13:34.410 --> 13:35.010
Sit down and have some more.

13:35.010 --> 13:35.530
Come on.

13:35.600 --> 13:36.240
No, no, it's fine.

13:36.260 --> 13:36.960
I'm full.

13:37.080 --> 13:38.010
I'll put the flowers over there.

13:40.340 --> 13:41.840
Your traditional Chinese medicine decoction is warm in the pot.

13:41.840 --> 13:42.940
Drink it while it's hot.

13:42.970 --> 13:44.330
Okay, got it.

13:45.810 --> 13:47.250
You know, that kid Yan

13:47.480 --> 13:48.530
is quite thoughtful.

13:48.530 --> 13:49.720
He always brings flowers.

13:50.010 --> 13:51.890
It's just that those flowers are too ugly.

13:53.300 --> 13:54.610
Why do I feel that

13:54.680 --> 13:56.930
when Ms. Shen's back, her mood is a bit...

13:58.230 --> 14:00.700
Did she get upset because Yan had something to do?

14:01.550 --> 14:02.520
Never mind.

14:02.800 --> 14:03.650
They've all grown up now.

14:03.840 --> 14:05.770
Let them solve some things on their own.

14:06.840 --> 14:08.600
There's no use in us worrying so much.

14:09.010 --> 14:10.320
Let them talk more when they have the time.

14:10.530 --> 14:12.840
Right, they're about to get married.

14:13.080 --> 14:14.010
What's there that can't be gotten over?"

14:14.010 --> 14:15.010
Exactly.

14:15.960 --> 14:16.800
How about...

14:18.470 --> 14:20.110
I break up with Yan Heng?

14:22.410 --> 14:23.250
Why?

14:23.720 --> 14:24.770
No, did Yan

14:24.770 --> 14:26.410
do something while on his business trip?

14:26.410 --> 14:27.010
No, no, nothing like that.

14:27.010 --> 14:28.080
You've been together for so long.

14:28.080 --> 14:29.370
How can you just break up like that?

14:29.370 --> 14:29.770
That's right.

14:29.770 --> 14:30.770
Who brought it up?

14:30.770 --> 14:31.600
No one did.

14:31.600 --> 14:32.560
What exactly happened...

14:32.560 --> 14:34.370
You call Yan now and ask him about it.

14:34.370 --> 14:35.320
How can I call him?

14:35.320 --> 14:36.600
You're a man.

14:36.600 --> 14:37.960
You should be the one to talk to him.

14:37.960 --> 14:39.600
I can't talk to him about this.

14:39.600 --> 14:40.290
If you can't talk to him,

14:40.290 --> 14:41.370
then I definitely can't...

15:21.800 --> 15:22.720
Yan Heng,

15:23.440 --> 15:26.080
I've been working at the hotel for nearly seven years.

15:26.720 --> 15:28.960
You never thought my work was bad before.

15:29.320 --> 15:30.650
Why do you now think

15:30.890 --> 15:32.270
my job embarrasses you?

15:37.720 --> 15:38.480
Yan Heng,

15:39.080 --> 15:40.630
please don't be angry anymore, okay?

15:41.200 --> 15:43.040
I didn't consider your feelings.

15:59.320 --> 16:00.080
It's freezing.

16:04.400 --> 16:07.490
Shen Xifan, it's exhausting being your boyfriend.

16:08.720 --> 16:09.480
You know how busy I am at work.

16:09.480 --> 16:11.050
Can't you be more considerate of me?

16:12.170 --> 16:13.770
You don't care about me at all.

16:13.770 --> 16:15.290
You only care about yourself.

16:16.000 --> 16:17.200
You're too selfish.

16:21.010 --> 16:22.480
I just love you too much.

16:22.720 --> 16:25.410
That's why I didn't realize you've always been this selfish.

16:25.680 --> 16:28.290
Whatever, I have nothing more to say.

16:28.290 --> 16:30.250
You don't appreciate my good intentions at all.

16:30.250 --> 16:31.170
You're too selfish!

16:31.720 --> 16:32.890
Why are you so selfish?

17:10.960 --> 17:11.890
Shen Xifan?

17:20.170 --> 17:21.569
Why are you sitting here all by yourself?

17:27.440 --> 17:28.610
I wanted to come down

17:29.090 --> 17:30.330
and be alone for a while.

17:38.200 --> 17:39.440
Didn't I tell you

17:39.440 --> 17:40.680
not to eat cold foods?

17:40.680 --> 17:41.680
Yet you're still eating this?

17:50.480 --> 17:51.090
Alright.

17:51.330 --> 17:52.610
Since you've already eaten so much,

17:52.890 --> 17:54.070
you might as well finish it all.

18:00.650 --> 18:01.930
It's already past eleven.

18:02.330 --> 18:03.330
Aren't you going to sleep yet?

18:03.570 --> 18:04.340
What?

18:04.590 --> 18:05.940
Isn't the medicine I prescribed for you working?

18:08.960 --> 18:10.000
It's working.

18:10.610 --> 18:14.040
I've been sleeping longer these past couple of days.

18:15.570 --> 18:18.130
Looks like the medicine I prescribed isn't the issue.

18:18.370 --> 18:19.810
It's you who hasn't been following the instructions.

18:31.090 --> 18:32.200
Have you encountered

18:32.360 --> 18:33.370
any troubles at work?

18:36.650 --> 18:37.410
No.

18:38.680 --> 18:39.520
Did you have a fight with someone?

18:46.760 --> 18:47.410
Your boyfriend?

19:06.930 --> 19:08.030
Actually...

19:09.170 --> 19:10.760
it's not really a fight.

19:11.440 --> 19:13.420
There are just some things

19:14.280 --> 19:15.960
that I can't figure out myself.

19:17.850 --> 19:18.560
It's my fault.

19:26.440 --> 19:28.460
Are you feeling...

19:28.930 --> 19:30.170
tight in the chest, upset,

19:30.190 --> 19:31.390
and in a bad mood right now?

19:33.520 --> 19:34.810
Come on, follow my lead.

19:35.440 --> 19:36.650
Hold out your right hand.

19:37.890 --> 19:38.720
Hold it out.

19:41.650 --> 19:43.330
Use the knuckle of your thumb

19:43.480 --> 19:44.240
to press

19:44.810 --> 19:46.850
the Danzhong acupoint in the middle of your chest.

19:55.280 --> 19:56.330
You're not pressing hard enough.

19:56.330 --> 19:56.930
Press harder.

19:56.930 --> 19:57.650
Otherwise, it won't be effective.

20:04.370 --> 20:05.240
It hurts.

20:06.810 --> 20:07.880
Does it hurt a lot?

20:10.130 --> 20:12.890
There's a saying in TCM that it hurts when it doesn't work.

20:13.240 --> 20:15.890
You're in pain because you have a troubled heart.

20:18.330 --> 20:21.200
So if I keep rubbing like this,

20:22.150 --> 20:24.040
will the pain go away?

20:28.680 --> 20:30.960
Pressing the Danzhong acupoint can only relieve symptoms.

20:31.270 --> 20:33.280
A troubled heart needs

20:33.610 --> 20:34.540
to be treated with heart medicine.

20:36.300 --> 20:38.270
Either clear the blockage,

20:40.890 --> 20:42.850
or remove the root cause of the illness.

20:48.370 --> 20:49.610
Remove the root cause?

21:08.480 --> 21:09.370
It's getting late.

21:09.370 --> 21:10.600
It's chilly outside at night.

21:10.690 --> 21:11.540
Don't catch a cold.

21:11.560 --> 21:12.430
Go home early.

21:13.130 --> 21:14.810
I won't bother you anymore then.

21:16.330 --> 21:17.130
I'll be going now.

21:18.000 --> 21:18.480
Okay.

21:23.000 --> 21:23.620
Oh, by the way,

21:24.440 --> 21:26.160
if you still can't sleep at night,

21:26.330 --> 21:27.850
put an apple by your bedside.

21:28.190 --> 21:30.310
The fragrance of the apple can help you sleep.

21:31.340 --> 21:33.300
Okay, thank you.

21:38.850 --> 21:39.960
Do you have apples at home?

21:42.440 --> 21:43.410
I think so.

21:45.690 --> 21:46.170
Alright.

21:46.520 --> 21:47.370
Well,

21:48.200 --> 21:49.400
see you at the next follow-up visit.

21:50.960 --> 21:52.000
See you at the follow-up.

21:53.850 --> 21:54.440
Good night.

21:55.960 --> 21:56.610
Good night.

21:58.910 --> 21:59.600
I'm leaving.

22:25.720 --> 22:26.960
I was just talking nonsense earlier.

22:26.960 --> 22:28.140
There's nothing going on.

22:31.680 --> 22:32.520
Really?

22:34.330 --> 22:35.350
You didn't have a fight, did you?

22:35.480 --> 22:36.370
No.

22:36.370 --> 22:38.170
I'm just too tired from work lately.

22:39.370 --> 22:40.810
Don't worry.

22:40.810 --> 22:41.810
Go to bed early, okay?

22:42.370 --> 22:42.930
Good night.

22:54.680 --> 22:55.330
Yan Heng,

22:55.930 --> 22:57.720
when will you be available?

22:58.090 --> 22:59.370
Let's have a talk.

23:00.440 --> 23:02.090
Whether it's through WeChat

23:02.370 --> 23:04.200
or talking face to face

23:04.440 --> 23:05.680
when you come back next time,

23:06.810 --> 23:08.330
When you see this WeChat message,

23:08.330 --> 23:09.810
please remember to reply to me.

23:22.230 --> 23:28.550
♫You're like a gentle wind♫

23:29.000 --> 23:34.550
♫After early summer afternoon, it blows past my heart♫

23:35.860 --> 23:42.050
♫When your fingers touch my hands♫

23:42.790 --> 23:47.400
♫So you're also here for me♫

23:46.200 --> 23:47.040
If you encounter any trouble at work,

23:47.040 --> 23:49.280
don't keep any worries to yourself.

23:49.480 --> 23:50.930
Don't put too much pressure on yourself.

23:49.810 --> 23:55.400
♫I hear you say, red beans grow in the southern lands♫

23:52.960 --> 23:54.090
Actually,

23:55.410 --> 23:57.090
at work,

23:56.380 --> 23:59.240
♫When spring comes, a few branches begin to sprout♫

23:59.000 --> 24:00.610
I don't have any troubles.

23:59.770 --> 24:03.240
♫Cherish the youth♫

24:02.370 --> 24:05.410
So, it's because of your boyfriend?

24:05.090 --> 24:11.010
♫Love you is the best thing I've ever done♫

24:08.720 --> 24:10.130
You're so blocked up.

24:11.480 --> 24:12.810
No wonder you can't sleep.

24:12.840 --> 24:18.050
♫Write it down in your heart and never disappear♫

24:30.330 --> 24:31.240
You're not drinking?

24:33.570 --> 24:36.950
Yesterday, I was secretly eating ice cream downstairs in the neighborhood,

24:37.000 --> 24:39.200
and Dr. He caught me red-handed.

24:39.480 --> 24:41.760
He specifically reminded me to watch my diet.

24:41.960 --> 24:43.480
In the neighborhood? At night?

24:45.000 --> 24:47.280
He works at a clinic near our neighborhood,

24:47.280 --> 24:48.960
so he lives in our neighborhood.

24:48.960 --> 24:50.130
That's pretty normal, isn't it?

24:51.370 --> 24:52.040
By the way,

24:52.070 --> 24:53.880
our hotel is about to host a summit.

24:54.130 --> 24:55.170
Zhongyu Group is going to

24:55.170 --> 24:56.810
hold a forum at this summit.

24:56.810 --> 24:57.850
Is Yan Heng coming?

25:00.410 --> 25:01.280
I don't know.

25:01.520 --> 25:02.630
I can't reach him.

25:09.930 --> 25:11.090
What's wrong with you?

25:13.760 --> 25:14.480
This is

25:14.480 --> 25:15.930
called Danzhong acupoint.

25:16.200 --> 25:17.810
If you massage it more,

25:17.810 --> 25:19.650
you can disperse the qi.

25:20.370 --> 25:22.520
This way, you won't feel so blocked up.

25:23.330 --> 25:24.460
Is this how you press it?

25:26.450 --> 25:27.600
I'll try it for a while too.

25:27.720 --> 25:29.130
I'm about to go crazy with all these

25:29.130 --> 25:30.520
various demands from the participating companies.

25:40.800 --> 25:46.060
[Hong'an Gate]

25:44.420 --> 25:45.570
Your complexion looks so bad.

25:45.810 --> 25:46.810
You didn't sleep well again, did you?

25:49.520 --> 25:51.280
Since that day,

25:51.600 --> 25:53.600
I haven't been able to sleep well.

25:57.370 --> 25:59.000
Come on, let me take your pulse.

26:00.440 --> 26:00.960
Okay.

26:11.410 --> 26:12.410
It's blocked again?

26:16.960 --> 26:19.120
Don't bear these emotions alone.

26:19.300 --> 26:20.130
Let it out.

26:20.160 --> 26:21.050
It's better than keeping it bottled up.

26:22.410 --> 26:24.040
I've been too busy lately.

26:24.760 --> 26:26.130
I don't have time to talk about this.

26:29.200 --> 26:29.820
It's alright.

26:30.610 --> 26:32.050
We can take it slow.

26:37.000 --> 26:38.040
You can trust my...

26:41.000 --> 26:41.680
Medical skills.

26:46.000 --> 26:47.440
I'll prescribe you some medicine to soothe your liver and regulate qi.

26:47.650 --> 26:49.280
It can help relieve some of your symptoms.

26:52.570 --> 26:53.570
But the most important thing

26:54.090 --> 26:55.680
is to untie the knot in your heart.

26:58.960 --> 27:00.280
I understand the reasoning.

27:02.560 --> 27:03.560
Have you tried acupuncture before?

27:08.040 --> 27:08.950
What's with that expression?

27:09.410 --> 27:10.280
Are you afraid of needles?

27:11.180 --> 27:13.510
I've never had it. I won't faint, I think.

27:14.240 --> 27:15.240
That's a pity.

27:15.270 --> 27:15.990
Otherwise,

27:16.210 --> 27:17.610
if you fainted, you could fall asleep right away.

27:18.720 --> 27:19.720
Acupuncture.

27:20.040 --> 27:21.800
I'll try on a few acupoints to calm your mind.

27:22.090 --> 27:24.490
After the acupuncture, you should be able to sleep more comfortably.

27:26.570 --> 27:27.130
Let's go.

27:27.850 --> 27:28.680
Prepare for acupuncture.

27:31.370 --> 27:32.890
You can even take a nap when you get back.

27:47.370 --> 27:48.330
Dr. He,

27:49.130 --> 27:50.760
how many needles are we going to use?

27:51.720 --> 27:52.760
A total of five acupoints.

27:53.200 --> 27:54.610
Don't be nervous. It's fine.

27:57.720 --> 27:58.440
Don't move.

27:59.110 --> 27:59.940
It's okay.

28:00.000 --> 28:00.760
Relax.

28:01.480 --> 28:02.280
We're starting.

28:03.380 --> 28:04.550
Relax.

28:08.130 --> 28:08.680
How is it?

28:08.480 --> 28:12.720
♫Two hearts♫

28:09.170 --> 28:09.890
Is it okay?

28:13.710 --> 28:18.480
♫We finally found each other♫

28:15.680 --> 28:16.760
Two acupoints on your hand.

28:17.610 --> 28:17.960
Okay.

28:22.070 --> 28:26.310
♫We'll never be apart again♫

28:23.680 --> 28:24.570
Disinfect first.

28:25.480 --> 28:26.240
Okay.

28:26.810 --> 28:31.410
♫Let's stick together like this♫

28:34.930 --> 28:39.830
♫You and I♫

28:41.410 --> 28:46.080
♫Be together♫

28:48.080 --> 28:52.830
♫You and I♫

28:54.100 --> 28:56.400
♫Now♫

28:59.520 --> 29:05.320
♫Never be apart♫

29:45.260 --> 29:46.330
Two more acupoints to go.

29:47.450 --> 29:48.130
Okay.

30:06.590 --> 30:07.390
The needles are all in place.

30:07.760 --> 30:09.170
The acupuncture treatment will take 15 minutes.

30:09.170 --> 30:10.000
You should rest for a while.

30:12.560 --> 30:14.150
Can I use my phone then?

30:15.170 --> 30:17.090
Why don't you consider closing your eyes and resting for a bit?

30:20.170 --> 30:21.040
Just lie down then.

30:21.170 --> 30:21.720
Okay.

31:35.010 --> 31:37.150
[TCM Room 3]

31:45.760 --> 31:46.610
She fell asleep.

32:30.750 --> 32:32.380
He, let's have dinner together.

32:33.230 --> 32:34.120
Let's eat at your place.

32:34.480 --> 32:35.520
You go ahead, I'll get the food.

32:35.520 --> 32:36.170
Okay.

33:02.590 --> 33:03.070
You're awake.

33:05.280 --> 33:06.610
How did I fall asleep?

33:07.440 --> 33:08.570
How long have I been sleeping?

33:09.200 --> 33:11.010
I gave you the acupuncture at 11:10.

33:11.090 --> 33:12.850
It's now 1:07.

33:13.930 --> 33:15.240
I slept for so long?

33:15.270 --> 33:15.930
I'm sorry.

33:15.930 --> 33:16.760
I've wasted your time.

33:16.760 --> 33:17.480
I'll leave now.

33:17.480 --> 33:18.330
Wait.

33:19.890 --> 33:21.200
Take this sachet.

33:23.040 --> 33:23.960
Sachet?

33:25.240 --> 33:26.680
It contains some herbs that can calm your nerves.

33:26.680 --> 33:28.170
It can help relieve your anxiety.

33:30.090 --> 33:31.130
It smells quite nice.

33:31.280 --> 33:31.760
Really?

33:32.130 --> 33:33.170
When you feel chest tightness or irritation,

33:33.170 --> 33:33.930
you can take a sniff of it.

33:33.930 --> 33:35.240
It'll definitely work better than an apple.

33:36.610 --> 33:37.930
Then I'll always carry it with me.

33:40.370 --> 33:42.260
But how much do these cost?

33:43.890 --> 33:44.510
This...

33:45.680 --> 33:46.410
This is free.

33:46.410 --> 33:47.280
It's a gift from me.

33:48.280 --> 33:48.760
Okay.

33:48.760 --> 33:49.500
Thank you.

33:52.570 --> 33:54.170
See you next Saturday then.

33:54.610 --> 33:54.960
Alright.

33:55.300 --> 33:56.060
I'm leaving.

33:57.130 --> 33:57.760
Bye.

35:20.350 --> 35:22.120
Are you writing this now?

35:22.600 --> 35:24.120
This is just an overall plan.

35:24.120 --> 35:25.690
We'll refine the details later.

35:26.210 --> 35:28.480
I still need to have a meeting with the Front Office staff later

35:28.730 --> 35:30.480
to review the room reservation system.

35:30.690 --> 35:32.770
This is my first major event

35:32.770 --> 35:34.640
as the new Front Office Manager.

35:34.640 --> 35:36.040
I must do it well.

35:37.480 --> 35:39.890
I hate these big events the most.

35:39.890 --> 35:41.850
The management come here for a vacation.

35:42.040 --> 35:43.440
While we, as service staff,

35:43.470 --> 35:44.670
are here to suffer.

35:45.530 --> 35:46.780
It's all your Marketing Department's fault.

35:47.000 --> 35:48.600
Why do you have to come up with so many fancy ideas?

35:48.960 --> 35:51.080
Can you stop being so smug when you're already getting the benefits?

35:51.370 --> 35:53.690
If our Marketing Department doesn't take on more big events,

35:53.690 --> 35:54.980
where would all those year-end bonuses come from?

35:55.930 --> 35:56.960
That's true.

35:57.520 --> 35:59.290
My study abroad agent told me today

35:59.290 --> 36:02.050
that my practical experience is still a bit thin.

36:02.370 --> 36:04.510
So I need experience with a large-scale event.

36:04.810 --> 36:06.210
If I can successfully complete

36:06.210 --> 36:07.440
this IT summit,

36:07.440 --> 36:07.850
then

36:07.850 --> 36:08.640
my chances of getting an offer

36:08.640 --> 36:09.480
will

36:09.480 --> 36:10.730
increase significantly.

36:11.410 --> 36:13.250
You're setting your standards too high.

36:13.440 --> 36:14.210
You insist on going to those

36:14.210 --> 36:15.410
top 3 schools.

36:15.560 --> 36:17.810
With so many competitors from all over the world,

36:17.810 --> 36:18.730
it's very difficult.

36:20.640 --> 36:21.850
I think

36:22.000 --> 36:24.000
if I'm going to spend money to study abroad,

36:24.000 --> 36:25.560
I should go to the best schools.

36:25.730 --> 36:26.850
Otherwise, it's meaningless.

36:26.850 --> 36:27.600
I agree.

36:37.850 --> 36:38.730
Are you planning to apply for

36:38.730 --> 36:40.410
the hospital's research funding this time?

36:40.960 --> 36:42.660
I'll definitely apply.

36:42.680 --> 36:43.680
I'm preparing the materials now.

36:44.330 --> 36:46.170
But I might not be able to apply for it.

36:46.810 --> 36:48.370
I did get it last year,

36:48.410 --> 36:50.690
but the hospital didn't pay much attention to it,

36:50.690 --> 36:51.960
so they didn't allocate much funding.

36:52.290 --> 36:55.400
Your main research direction is too niche.

36:55.690 --> 36:57.960
Palliative care in TCM oncology,

36:57.960 --> 37:00.440
isn't it just end-of-life care, to put it bluntly?

37:00.440 --> 37:01.640
It's hard to see immediate results.

37:02.040 --> 37:03.770
Only someone with great compassion like you

37:03.770 --> 37:05.040
can persist for so many years.

37:05.040 --> 37:06.850
I truly admire you from the bottom of my heart.

37:06.850 --> 37:09.640
And our hospital's funding is limited,

37:09.640 --> 37:12.290
so the management can only allocate it this way, right?

37:12.520 --> 37:13.410
Yes, indeed.

37:17.040 --> 37:19.840
You could ask Professor Yu to endorse your application.

37:19.860 --> 37:21.150
You'll definitely get the funding then,

37:21.440 --> 37:22.930
and probably more of it too.

37:23.680 --> 37:24.510
Forget it.

37:24.890 --> 37:27.080
Professor Yu has so many teaching tasks that he can't finish them all.

37:27.370 --> 37:28.480
I won't bother him.

37:28.770 --> 37:29.740
Alright.

37:38.640 --> 37:40.440
Why are you asking me about all this today?

37:41.570 --> 37:43.090
I care about you.

37:46.560 --> 37:47.080
Speak up.

37:47.480 --> 37:48.600
What do you really want to say?

37:49.410 --> 37:50.040
It's like this.

37:50.410 --> 37:52.040
There's a blind date event tonight.

37:52.040 --> 37:53.930
It's all doctors and nurses from the First Hospital.

37:53.930 --> 37:55.080
They're short two men.

37:55.080 --> 37:56.440
I want you to come with me

37:56.440 --> 37:57.890
to give me some courage.

37:59.290 --> 38:00.250
I'm not going.

38:00.500 --> 38:01.750
I haven't even finished writing my research proposal.

38:02.250 --> 38:04.640
When can't you write that proposal?

38:04.640 --> 38:06.040
You're not getting any younger, you know.

38:06.040 --> 38:08.520
It's time to start thinking about your personal issues.

38:08.520 --> 38:09.210
You should find...

38:09.210 --> 38:10.080
I think

38:10.080 --> 38:11.520
you should find someone from our hospital.

38:11.520 --> 38:12.600
Then you can go to work and leave work together.

38:12.600 --> 38:14.600
It's so convenient. Why bother with blind dates?

38:15.000 --> 38:17.290
Ah, you're no fun.

38:17.600 --> 38:18.890
How can you pour cold water on me like that?

38:18.960 --> 38:20.440
I really want to stop being single.

38:57.100 --> 38:57.970
Xifan,

38:58.520 --> 38:59.690
I've been thinking for a long time.

39:00.160 --> 39:01.230
We should break up.

39:18.470 --> 39:22.130
[The other party has rejected.]

41:36.350 --> 41:44.250
[Yan Heng]

41:45.080 --> 41:46.520
Why don't you just delete me?

41:50.960 --> 41:54.540
♫Even if we're destined to meet and miss each other♫

41:54.000 --> 41:55.730
Did she have another fight with her boyfriend?

41:54.750 --> 42:00.800
♫Life is finally complete♫
